.TH AGENT-HOOK-POST-EDIT 1 "2026-06-30" "agentguard" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
agent-hook-post-edit \- format edited files through Sley
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B agent-hook-post-edit
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B agent-hook-post-edit
reads an agent edit hook JSON payload from standard input and delegates changed
files to
.BR "sley hook format-file" .
Broader lint and verification remain native commit-hook responsibilities so
human and agent commit workflows share the same readiness path.
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Formatting completed, selected formatter failures were ignored after Sley
surfaced them, or no format target was selected.
.TP
.B 2
The local install is missing required dependencies such as
.BR sley .
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR agent-hook-pre-edit (1),
.BR sley (1)
